ync" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Robbie-Williams-and-Cher.-Credit-Don-Arnold-and-Mike-Marsland-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Robbie-Williams-and-Cher.-Credit-Don-Arnold-and-Mike-Marsland-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Robbie-Williams-and-Cher.-Credit-Don-Arnold-and-Mike-Marsland-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Robbie-Williams-and-Cher.-Credit-Don-Arnold-and-Mike-Marsland-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Robbie-Williams-and-Cher.-Credit-Don-Arnold-and-Mike-Marsland-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Robbie-Williams-and-Cher.-Credit-Don-Arnold-and-Mike-Marsland-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artist/robbie-williams">罗比·威廉姆斯</a>公开了他与<a href="/artists/Cher">雪儿的尴尬和“粗鲁”的遭遇，</a>称这让他事后“用头撞墙”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/robbie-williams-review-netflix-3532889">《罗比·威廉姆斯》评论：Netflix 医生明确了流行歌星的危险</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位“天使”歌手于周一（5 月 27 日）在他的官方 Instagram 帐户上分享了他最近与这位流行传奇人物在机场的相遇。他是由一位共同的朋友介绍给雪儿的，他透露自己的社交尴尬已经全面爆发。</p><p>他写道：“我想让她的互动尽可能轻松。为了在谈话中寻找一个自然的休息或结束，我找借口坐下来。这不是为了我，而是为了她。唉，我认为雪儿还没说完，这让我退出我们短暂的互动显得很粗鲁。当然，在接下来的25年里，我会时不时地想起这一刻。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7d1KUaK8HL/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-rig